      "message": "\u003e ScopedMachVM doesn\u0027t do vm_read does it?\n\nNo, it doesn’t do anything that allocates at all, but you can give it some Mach-allocated memory and it’ll own deallocation. (But it doesn’t guarantee RUNS-AT-CRASH safety.)",
